{"tid":1964864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟香港嗰二百幾萬黃絲幾時先肯一齊參與twitter戰線？","createTime":"2020-04-09T06:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T05:59:06.000Z","uid":149494,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2be68e3572fb4639e719132613dffd47d28e43","tid":1964864,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"而家twitter戰線唔好話二百幾萬黃絲<br />\n連二萬都唔知有無<br />\n呢班咁既人唔好話叫佢地企前線<br />\n連留響屋企嗰陣叫佢地參與twitter戰線都唔肯<br />\n而家根本係歷史上最好既時機比你地打國際線唱衰中共<br />\n個個寧願浪費時間響屋企打機/IG story/煲劇/睇電子雞都唔肯幫手上twitter唱衰中共<br />\n香港人真心唔配贏,無資格贏<br />\n係抵撚死的"},{"pid":"cfe179645894b9fb04c7a28588e95b63a694220e","tid":1964864,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"12d305f7f35840609666fb6bc69ec2be6aaad1ca","tid":1964864,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:26:49.000Z","msg":"做文宣叫大家幫手打twitter戰線啦<br />\n放乜野負<br />\n居心叵測呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過你個大名好多人都識"},{"pid":"658f5f781627b1c3523d94835bc3bf1e8238b857","tid":1964864,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"香港就算二百幾萬黃絲總動員上場<br />\n都未必敵得過海外五毛/左膠 <br />\n但起碼有力一戰先<br />\n但香港人就係咁撚垃圾<br />\n連咁簡單既野都唔肯做<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"7679b742a2b76cc94e7f6f550b1b23ec98f506a1","tid":1964864,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=17d3e06a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n比個like同retweet都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5 秒都唔洗"},{"pid":"b372570da217185312cdb22f2ab0ae2d4ed52cbb","tid":1964864,"uid":160551,"like":0,"di